org.knime.core.node.port

Class PortObjectZipOutputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.OutputStream
      • java.io.FilterOutputStream
        • java.util.zip.DeflaterOutputStream
          • java.util.zip.ZipOutputStream
            • org.knime.core.node.port.PortObjectZipOutputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, Flushable, AutoCloseable

    public class PortObjectZipOutputStream
extends ZipOutputStream
    Zip stream that is used to persist objects of class PortObject. Its current implementation offers the functionality provided by an ZipOutputStream; it is a separate class to enable future customization (for instance by adding methods that are needed in future versions of KNIME).

    This class is not meant to be instantiated by ordinary node implementations. This class may change without notice.

    Author:
    Bernd Wiswedel, University of Konstanz
